Asian
Studies professor Livia Kohn on a wonderful hike to the temples and
mountains
of Kyoto, Japan. Enjoy beautiful scenery, spectacular foliage,
delicious food,
and steaming hot tubs while learning first-hand about Japanese culture,
religion, and lifestyle.
 
